author: Joi-Marie McKenzie
title: Have Amanda Seyfried and Justin Long Split?
text:
Lloyd Bishop/NBC (LOS ANGELES) -- Amanda Seyfried and Justin Long have reportedly gone their separate ways. 
According to a source, the two "are breaking up," reports The New York Post 's Page Six. 
"He wanted to get married, she wasnâ€™t ready to make the commitment," another source added. 
Back in June, Seyfried told Vogue why her relationship with Long worked. "I really do have my own identity, both inside and outside the relationship, if that makes any sense. It just feels right. It's also really good to feel OK being alone," she said . 
The couple went public with their romance two years ago. Seyfried said previously the two met via mutual friends in the summer of 2013.
